	<section class="article-content clearfix" itemprop="articleBody">
		<p>Persivia’s Network Performance solution provides actionable insights into the cost, use, and efficiency of your physicians to help reduce physician practice pattern variation and promote value-based, pay-for-performance reimbursement models.</p>
<p>Persivia provides credible, reliable and effective provider analytics by delivering analytics around both primary and specialty care physicians and enables users to better manage and monitor the efficiency and quality of health care provided by physicians.</p>
<p>Delivered on the Persivia platform, an industry-leading solution for aggregating, analyzing and reporting clinical data sets, this solution empowers all healthcare stakeholders — including clinicians — to manage care. This is achieved by providing the right information, to the right person, at the precise moment in time when the quality and cost of care have the greatest impact.</p>
<p>The Network Performance Management solution helps to maintain clinical and operational consistency, while providing enhancements in quality and cost control for patients and populations.</p>
<h4>Persivia’s Network Performance Solution Includes:</h4>
<ul>
<li>Provider profiling</li>
<li>Clinically-based utilization reporting</li>
<li>Utilization rates across settings</li>
<li>Incorporates claims and clinical data</li>
<li>Physician Cost Efficiency Scores</li>
<li>Physician specific costs (per patient, per episode, etc.)</li>
<li>Total cost per patient</li>
<li>Total Lab, Radiology &amp; Pharmacy Costs</li>
</ul>	</section>
	
